The '''Lycinder Plain''' was a flat area on the equator of [[Troiken/Legends|Troiken]], located in front of [[Mount Avos]]. In [[44 BBY/Legends|44 BBY]] after the [[First Battle of Qotile]] [[Outland Regions Security Force/Legends|Ranulph Tarkin's paramilitary]] landed there to evacuate into the mountain.

==Behind the scenes==
It is misspelled "Lycinder ''Plan''" in the comic.

